Package: energy.gov
Title: Department of Energy Data Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for DOE energy data. Alternative fuel stations
    (EV, CNG, LPG, hydrogen) via the NREL AFDC API. FITARA IT milestones.
    Requires API key for AFDC (DEMO_KEY works for testing).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, jsonlite, dplyr, tibble
